    //Open and close more options at the the of the page...
    //I tried getting a nice transition effect, but with the way I have done the search at the top (Absolute position), pushing the content below

    $(document).ready(function () {

        var $options = $('#moreOptions, #lessOptions');
        var $arrow = $('.arrow-down, .arrow-up');

        $('#moreOptions').click(function () {

            $('.searchBox--box .searchBox--text').toggle();
            $('.searchBox--box .divider').addClass('divider--high');
            $($options).toggle();
            $($arrow).toggle();
        });

        $('#lessOptions').click(function () {
            
            $('.searchBox--box .searchBox--text').toggle();
            $('.searchBox--box .divider').removeClass('divider--high');
            $($options).toggle();
            $($arrow).toggle();
        });

    });
</script>
